Tamagit tlla bdda dar ufgan kra yga, zund aɣgan izdɣn g ṭṭalyan, tamagit-nes tga taṭalyanit, tlla daɣ tamagit tafṛanṣiṣt, taɛṛabt, [[tamaziɣt]] ...
Kra yga wfgan dars tamagit-nes, ur jju ylla wfgan bla tamagit.
Tamagit n ufgan ar tskar kigan n tmukrisin ger middn,acku kud yan dayttini tamagit inu ayḥlan.
